<i>clouds of war gather over Europe.</i>

2
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:25,758
<i>But here in Navarre, the King, seen here</i>
<i>returning from military manoeuvres,...</i>

3
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:29,117
<i>..has announced an audacious plan</i>
<i>for himself and his court.</i>

4
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:34,309
<i>He and his companions will cast off their</i>
<i>military uniforms, while events allow,...</i>

5
00:02:34,560 --> 00:02:38,109
<i>..and devote themselves to three years'</i>
<i>study. That's right - three years.</i>

6
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:43,992
<i>They'll sleep little, eat less, and devote</i>
<i>themselves instead to self-improvement:</i>

7
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:46,276
<i>..a real feast for bookworms.</i>

8
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:51,116
<i>Boldest is the King's insistence that no</i>
<i>women will be allowed inside the court.</i>

9
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:53,191
<i>Sorry, ladies, but he is the king.</i>

10
00:02:53,440 --> 00:02:57,399
<i>There is just one exception: Madam</i>
