<i>themselves from thoughts of romance.</i>

13
00:03:06,200 --> 00:03:07,428
<i>Whoops! Careful, sir.</i>

14
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:12,231
<i>lt's a tall order, but this able monarch,</i>
<i>one of Europe's most eligible bachelors,..</i>

15
00:03:12,480 --> 00:03:15,517
<i>..wants to show the world</i>
<i>there's more to life than warfare.</i>

16
00:03:15,760 --> 00:03:18,991
<i>He's an idealist, but we wish him</i>
